                            <comment id="75643" author="yujian" created="Sun, 26 Jan 2014 09:22:47 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The failure did not occur regularly on Lustre b2_5 branch. Two more test sessions showed that the same test passed on build #16 and #15:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/59e43998-8616-11e3-a2cb-52540035b04c&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/59e43998-8616-11e3-a2cb-52540035b04c&lt;/a&gt; (build #16)&lt;br/&gt;
